KNN
---
make weeds PARAMETERS=reduced-parameters.csv TRAINING=training-521.csv ML=knn

Decision Tree
-------------
make weeds PARAMETERS=reduced-parameters.csv TRAINING=training-521.csv ML=decision

Boosted Gradient
----------------
make weeds PARAMETERS=reduced-parameters.csv TRAINING=training-521.csv ML=gradient

Random Forest
-------------
make weeds PARAMETERS=reduced-parameters.csv TRAINING=training-521.csv ML=forest
